title: Social Studies TASC Practice Test 4
intro_text:
Social Studies

Welcome to the Social Studies Practice Test!

This test is about half the length of an official TASC Test. You have 37 minutes to complete the 24 test questions.

The goal is to give you practice on the types of questions you will see on the TASC Test.

If you are unsure of an answer, click “Review Question Later” to come back to the question later.
